b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":1909,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"A New High-Difficulty Quest, Morsayati Reckoning, Has Been Added!","message":"<div>A new high-difficulty quest, Morsayati Reckoning, was added to the Forgotten Truths raid event at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1610604000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>In this quest, players will square off against Morsayati, a powerful raid boss with no elemental attunement. This quest is available to challenge at any time and may be attempted in both solo- and co-op play by spending stamina and getherwings.<\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/7a5f63a03ed928f01357fd5345f02f88.png\\"><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Clear this quest to earn Fortifying Dragonscales and Amplifying Dragonscales to augment your dragons and Nature&#39;s Blessings, a material necessary for leveling up facilities.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Quest Skill<\/div><div>If the miasma gauge fills up completely during the battle, Morsayati will become even more powerful, so use the quest skill to deplete it before his power overwhelms you!<\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a2623ea5a838c59c6860051b496d6ff5.png\\"><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Weekly Bonuses<\/div><div>Fortifying Dragonscales and Amplifying Dragonscales may be obtained as weekly bonuses for the Morsayati Reckoning quest.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Facility Level Caps<\/div><div>The maximum level of certain facilities was increased at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1610604000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The following facilities may be leveled up to 45:<\/div><div>\\u30fbFlame Altar<\/div><div>\\u30fbWater Altar<\/div><div>\\u30fbWind Altar<\/div><div>\\u30fbLight Altar<\/div><div>\\u30fbShadow Altar<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The following facilities may be leveled up to 40:<\/div><div>\\u30fbSword Dojo<\/div><div>\\u30fbBlade Dojo<\/div><div>\\u30fbDagger Dojo<\/div><div>\\u30fbAxe Dojo<\/div><div>\\u30fbLance Dojo<\/div><div>\\u30fbBow Dojo<\/div><div>\\u30fbWand Dojo<\/div><div>\\u30fbStaff Dojo<\/div><div>\\u30fbManacaster Dojo<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Other<\/div><div>The Nature&#39;s Blessing material has been added to the Wyrmsigil Remnants section of the Treasure Trade.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. Players must have viewed the epilogue for the Forgotten Truths event in the Event Compendium in order to attempt the Morsayati Reckoning quest.<\/div><div>2. Raid boosts and event perks have no effect in the Morsayati Reckoning raid battle.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1610604000,"prev_article_id":"10056","next_article_id":"1907","image_path":"","update_time":1610587627}}}'